These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, tiparillo, swisher, ritmeester
4 different pets are kept: turtle, hedgehog, hamster, cat
There 4 different types of food: apple, cucumber, cabbage, cherry
City: new-york, marseilles, miami, hannover
4 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, billiard, mah-jongg
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, daffodil, azalea, orchid
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, grey, green, purple
 1. the cain-smoker is the person traveling to new-york##1
 2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 3. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 4. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
 5. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 6. the person who likes black is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 7. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
 8. the person playing billiard is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 9. the person who likes purple is the person playing scrabble##1
10. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person eating apple##1
11. the person who growssunflower is the tiparillo-smoker##1
12. the person who likes grey is the person playing billiard##1
13. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
14. the person who growsdaffodil is the ritmeester-smoker##1
15. the person who growsorchid is the person eating cabbage##1
16. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person eating apple##1
17. the swisher-smoker is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4      |
| Cigar      | cain       | ritmeester      | swisher       | tiparillo    |
| Pet         | turtle    | cat    | hedgehog      | hamster    |
| Food           | cherry | apple       | cabbage | cucumber     |
| City   | new-york         | miami  | hannover      | marseilles     |
| Game   | scrabble          | mah-jongg     | billiard       | snooker |
| Flower         | azalea       | daffodil | orchid       | sunflower   |
| Color     | purple     | green  | grey         | black   |

