The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, volleyball, biathlon, handball
4 different games are played: canasta, whist, scrabble, bridge
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, paramedic, software-developer, firefighter
House: futuristic, modern, cottage, art-deco
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, lemonade, iced-tea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, bolivar, tiparillo, blend
 1. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 2. the modern house is on the right of the software-developer##1
 3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 4. the software-developer is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 5. the firefighter is the person playing whist##1
 6. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 7. the freelancer is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the person playing scrabble is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 9. the futuristic house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
12. the art-deco house is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
13. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
14. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
15. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
16. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
17. the art-deco house is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3      |      4      |
